The Quaker Oats Co said it soldits Vernell's Fine Candies Inc unit to privately-held KeystonePartners Inc for an undisclosed price.    The company said Vernells had sales of around 30 mln dlrsin the year ended in August, 1986.    Quaker Oats acquired Vernells in August, 1986 when itpurchased Golden Grain Macaroni Co.    Reuter&#3;